text:
The Career Day is the day when companies have the chance to meet all our participants and select their top candidates to invite for an onsite interview.

**13 May 2020,** [**CVCI**](https://www.google.ch/maps/place/Chambre+vaudoise+du+commerce+et+de+l'industrie/@46.5102397,6.6265574,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x478c2fce346e302b:0xd9d3a4e5317a32e6!8m2!3d46.510236!4d6.6287461) (**Vaud Chamber of Commerce and Industry), Lausanne**
title: Career Day Lausanne
